{"tid":1118839,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"森美MJ齊否認：工作以外無見心穎","createTime":"2019-04-21T14:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T17:12:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4cf51426fbade7afd0a152d23a0fcc6ea42f35f","tid":1118839,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190421/s00009/82b81732e6118e554bec8392625466d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190421%2Fs00009%2F82b81732e6118e554bec8392625466d7.jpg&h=472c9a80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃心穎與許志安車廂偷食事件，震驚全城。黃心穎形象盡毀，有關她的負面傳聞接踵而來，有報道指有鄰居爆料說看到有不同圈中人出入黃心穎香閨，其中有一名商台男主持，跟黃心穎十指緊扣返家，在電梯內舉止親暱；另一個是成日劃眼線的組合結他手，而該組合快將開演唱會。網民隨即猜測誰是疑似人物，令森美與樂隊Mr.的譚傑明（MJ）被牽涉其中。森美曾與黃心穎合作《學是學非》及《森美旅行團》，又讚好黃心穎道歉文被網民鬧爆。<br />\n<br />\n森美對此否認，強調沒有在私底下或工作以外同心穎見面，所以嫌疑人不是他。MJ亦說不是他，他雖然跟心穎認識多年，但從來無單獨見面，多是工作上成班人一齊，亦不知心穎住那處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190421/1555855582532/%E3%80%90%E5%82%B3%E5%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E8%A8%AA%E9%A6%99%E9%96%A8%E3%80%91%E6%A3%AE%E7%BE%8Emj%E9%BD%8A%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%8B%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190421%2F1555855582532%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E9%2596%25A8%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E7%25BE%258Emj%25E9%25BD%258A%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A9%258E&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5ROm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=1db29b51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190421%2F1555855582532%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25